{"name": "Lyn Boyd", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/people/Lyn-Boyd/100013568586343?hc_ref=ARRvGJ4wWOJLiG8qbiioA80gI-4Lc-tSg-08m21VkS-_To3gAvAlXsXCvbKnG6-pg0I&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>With so much negativity and poor service about, I would actually like to say thank you for excellent service today Energy Australia, starting with the efficient and pleasant woman who took my call about a regulator fault I had. After taking details I was told the fault would be looked at within 48 to 72 hours. To my surprise it was attended to and fixed within a few hours. No cold shower tomorrow - thank you!</p>", "timestamp": "21 August"}
{"name": "Wal Mills", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Can't believe this company. Got a letter today 21 Aug to say rates changed on 2 July. Says I'll probably pay more because distributor/network company have changed rates. I'm on time of use rates. Ausgrid chart attached shows no Peak rates, only shoulder and off-peak for non-summer and non winter periods but EA prices show Peak rates and only off-peak and shoulder as 'if applicable'. Tried to ring them for an explanation on the number supplied (1800) but the person in Manila c<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">ould not understand so I asked to be transferred to any nationality in Australia, but after after a number of attempts ended back there again and again. Then rang their 1300 number, got Manila again but ended transferred back in Australia only to be told it was above their knowledge and would transfer me to an account specialist who ended up back in Manila. I gave up in the end after speaking to several people and over an hour on the phone<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fc/1/16/1f620.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\ude20</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fc/1/16/1f620.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\ude20</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fc/1/16/1f620.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\ude20</span></span></span></p>", "timestamp": "20 August"}
