{"name": "Debra Hustwaite", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>We are building a new home and have no choice at the moment other than Energy Australia /Powercor to have a new meter connected. After waiting 37 minutes this morning to speak to one of your consultants it makes me wonder what your service will be like as our energy provider. Not looking good is it ? <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fc8/1/16/1f440.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\udc40</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f95/1/16/1f629.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\ude29</span></span></p>", "timestamp": "3 April"}
