{"name": "Irene Howard", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Paid deposit and signed a contract for solar install in Lithgow on 4/12/17 was told by email it would be installed within 4 to 6 weeks maximum , still waiting as they lost their installers in the entire area , so they were going ahead with my meter change out and working on getting a new installer ! stayed home waiting on meter exchange to happen , called Energy Australia on the day of meter change out only to be told that they now no longer have anyone to do the meter change out , as the weather is getting nasty here and I have no economical way to heat my home I am getting angry , anyone in the area also having this problem ? Oh also told they have no way of knowing how much longer this could drag on for .</p>", "timestamp": "25 February"}
