{"name": "Ravind Pandeer", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>I am beyond disappointed. I\u2019ve just moved in to a new apartment where the electricity had been disconnected prior to my moving in, and after several phone calls, an after hours team (for an extra charge) was supposed to come to the property to connect my electricity/turn on the Meter switch and was asked to be at the property until midnight. Midnight came and went and nobody had turned up and my apartment remained without power. And to make things worse, I had to put my life on hold for 5 hours in the darkness when I could have been comfortable somewhere else.</p>", "timestamp": "12 February"}
