{"name": "Chris Adams", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/people/Chris-Adams/581559370?hc_ref=ARQtcEfUIPRk9S-KZ3YvRfutk8Ka3syUaslekh4p1EzyoUaUHiEakwUlklPvEpvW1uk&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Quick update Danielle called me and pretended to fix the issue and re signed me up the the CORRECT meter and promised me that she would organise me an out of hours service for before midnight tonight. I was advise if I hadn't heard by 9pm to call and check with Ausgrid 9:30PM comes and I called Ausgrid to find that in fact Danielle had not done anything she said she would and no tech was scheduled so I am to spend the whole night with no power and this is all because Energy Australia advised ausgrid to connect the wrong unit number up absolute disgrace of a company this is, go somewhere else for your power needs. They have no out of hours customer care.</p>", "timestamp": "3 October 2017"}
