{"name": "Chris Adams", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/people/Chris-Adams/581559370?hc_ref=ARTlAkcXFo0fyV7pfYfS_e6IQYmiSO4KoW3NDRCKNluPWDT3Ytsi8FGM8vOTbgx9jx0&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>I signed up with you a month ago got an account number and my meter was read. Today you instructed my power to be turned off for no reason. I have called your line and they hung up on me after giving me no help. Someone needs to get here and switch the power back on. On the ASAP I am not spending the night with no power.</p>", "timestamp": "2 October 2017"}
