{"name": "Erin Carolan", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Just got an $1100 gas bill. For a 2 bedroom apartment! I don't think so. Waited on the line for half an hour, got through to someone who put me through to another department - no warm transfer or anything. Now been waiting another 20 mins. If you tell me I'm progressing in the queue or my time is precious one more time I may scream.</p>", "timestamp": "11 September 2017"}
{"name": "Andrew Galpin", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Hi there, <br> I was just on hold with Energy Australia for 33 minutes, because the account for our house is not actually in my name, they want to talk to the account holder who isn't here right now. Ive asked them to call back tomorrow, but the person I spoke to will be in training for the next week or so and won't be able to call me back. She cant get anyone else in all of Energy Australia to call me back tomorrow. No one. So if I REALLY REALLY want to stay with energy Australia, I will need to call back and wait in a queue again. <br> If you wish to treat your customers so poorly then we will not remain your customer.</p>", "timestamp": "11 September 2017"}
