{"name": "Terry Jones", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Hi anybody at all at energy Australia how long do i have to wait for a promised call from you people?Tried to call that was hopeless ,tried your online chat ,was told sorry cant help you ,will email sales team to contact you asap .What has happened to this company i have been a customer for years and never never have experienced such appalling lack of service from simply negative staff attitude.</p>", "timestamp": "4 September 2017"}
{"name": "Robyn Martin", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Thanks energy australia for putting me in debt with my gas, I have for a long time paid fortnightly payment one to electricity and one to gas, but on your end both payments have gone on electricity only, I have made several calls for your end to rectify this. I was told it is fixed. No its not, yet again 3 calls to you today with no fixing it your end. It shows on my payments that it goes to both gas and power, but not on statements from you I have no options left but to find another supplier, I cant pay the debt you created me on the gas bill . And your people don't seem to understand to fix it. Ps I won't be paying whats owing as you created that gas debt and won't transfer the payment I paid for gas from the electricity account</p>", "timestamp": "4 September 2017"}
{"name": "Justine Nguy", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Absolutely the worst service ever! My electricity usage has also been incorrectly calculated and I am being charged nearly triple the average amount on ALL my past bills with ZERO changes to lifestyle and appliances and being 11 hours away from home everyday. I have spoken to 2 customer service reps and they have BOTH advised me the wrong information - to email enq@energyaustralia.com.au with a photo of my meter - so much as to \"assure\" me that my issue will be fixed. Yet, wh<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">en I received a reply from Enquiries, I have been told \"I apologise if Marcel advised for you to send a photo of your meter read, with the type of meter that you have we wouldn't be able to accept meter reads since reads are remotely and digitally transferred to us during the end of a billing period\". What nonsense is this?! Rest assured I will be taking this case to the Ombudsman if you do not resolve my problem yet again.</span></p>", "timestamp": "4 September 2017"}
{"name": "Stephanie Jarred", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>I received my bill today and it was triple what it has been over the last two years. I was on hold for 10 mins and then you hung up on me. I've called back and on hold for over 10 mins again. I've been a customer for the last 8 years. Coincidently there's a brand new meter suddenly at our house too. There's no way we suddenly tripled out usage. Can someone please get back to me.</p>", "timestamp": "4 September 2017"}
