{"name": "Nilanke Ratnayake", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Hi, I made an enquiry with you guys to have my meter changed so that it can measure off peak readings (ref 5501085252). Since I didnt hear back from you I called you guys again today and I was told that I need to get an electrician and get the meter changed myself. I also had a conversation with one of your live chat staff and he said this information is wrong and the only people that can change the meter are the electricity distributors (I have the chat transcript). So I spoke to the distributor and they said meter changes are done by electricity retailers. Can someone please let me know how to get my meter changed so that I dont have to pay a $1000 bill to Energy Australia for a house where only 2 people live???</p>", "timestamp": "29 August 2017"}
{"name": "Lily Hatcher-Hilden", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/lily.solameithurts?hc_ref=ART5Fbxvvx50GC5OVNE_u75ly3kV09AQFwahvHpjglHC2Rt0mqrObSifKMVDg_9_qHw&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>I have currently been on hold for over 30 minutes. </p>", "timestamp": "29 August 2017"}
{"name": "Brooklynn Grant", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/brooklynn.grant.7?hc_ref=ARQ16FkH4Ky5EcnaMr-h-PulL5yD7VA070lg3COS3xkBtQvNIVoBqxsZISLMg8YyCxw&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>After being on hold to your call centre for 20 minutes I gave up and decided to voice my grievance here. <br> I have been a customer of Energy Australia on TWO entirely separate occasions at TWO entirely separate addresses.<br> My current address' account was opened by my builder and in turn put in my name as I took possession of the property. <br> I have not ONCE received a gas bill to this address, not via post and not via email (which is my preferred) so after calling 3 times to recti<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">fy this as all I ever get is an OVERDUE text.. <br> finally your operator on my last call advised me that you were POSTING (wrong) the bills to the first address (also wrong) that had absolutely nothing to do with this account (it wasn't a change of address, it wasn't a postal address ever) <br> So he assured me it was all resolved.. he changed the address to my actual address and changed my preferred billing method to the correct one.<br> .. so he says.</span></p>", "timestamp": "29 August 2017"}
{"name": "EnergyAustralia", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?hc_ref=ARRVPN0A1nH2vHnK-ukS2hj4SHUALHS2uEYx1yWqkWYjWNSHDM9M01yJScaklgkrLYk", "comment": "<p>NECA Members can save 35% off their electricity usage by contacting <a class=\"profileLink\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=mentions\">EnergyAustralia</a>. For more info visit <a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fneca.asn.au%2Fvic%2Fenergyaustralia&amp;h=AT0WdzuKyxWNmciNw2M2grttPOypMsF5CZ_18-GOA17RWD4M6fFxJdDVRPKh3YYhLQ7pKKgTSJznqcZWoWVkJ8Qvr6iUK65ByeV1TxD4vzOssYWsAnBtsOqM1fZUnfBMD-d3pk9ggi_xYJr31XnBsAIFylW_EWBY-lEr2E_C\" target=\"_blank\" data-ft='{\"tn\":\"-U\"}' rel=\"nofollow\" data-lynx-mode=\"hover\">https://neca.asn.au/vic/energyaustralia</a></p>", "timestamp": "29 August 2017"}
