{"name": "Hao Nguyen", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Hi Energy Australia,<br> I've been a customer of yours for quite a number of years... probably over 10 years.<br> I moved away from my old property close to 18 months ago in which I had a Gas Account which i closed the account after I moved.<br> To my surprise, i have been receiving bills for this gas account every quarter and taking money out of my account via direct debit. Each time I've called to sort this out they said it has been sorted but up to now it hasn't been resolved. <br> I am seriously now considering changing service providers.</p>", "timestamp": "31 July 2017"}
