{"name": "Gordon Gapes", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Just paid my bill with my credit card. Thanks for broadcasting all my entered private details back to me &amp; any one else within earshot. Well done in taking away our security with this broadcasting, why not just put it on a spread sheet for more to find out, well done. Do not even attempt to message me back with rubbish waffle, just simply STOP IT &amp; I wont give you access to my accounts for direct debit, as they are MY private areas, not yours. If you refuse to do what is right &amp; correct &amp; stop telling all others our PRIVATE details, I will have no other recourse in taking the matter to the privacy commission. <br> JUST STOP IT!</p>", "timestamp": "10 July 2017"}
