{"name": "Amy Dave Williamson", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>I was supposed to have my gas and electricity connected on the 19th of January 2017 for when I moved into my new house on the 21st of January... i walk in to my new house to test the lights only to find there was NO power on  at all and the electricians card still there from when he disconnected it in october 2016. I completed the online request as asked and selected my connection date. I called your 24hour service line todayand was told that there wasn't even a supply order requested for my new address! REALLY NOT HAPPY, luckily I have relative that I can stay with otherwise I would be sending you the bill for a hotel room!</p>", "timestamp": "21 January 2017"}
