{"name": "Roger Goold", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/rgoold1?hc_ref=ARSrx0JPPf4b_ja18d-y3fadzjzw31eeYbtfLJ79Hpsulbsg4zaJjswWyxXuTYP42wQ&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Thank you two cinema tickets...NOT  I got sent this card as an apology for REALLY BAD SERVICE, but when i finally got round to try and redeem it and get cinema tickets, I was told that as I hadn't registered in 30 days they had expired, and then the operator Gumpta hung up when I asked to speak to a supervisor...So it seems that there is a time limit on an apology form Energy Australia, and after that they don't give a monkeys...</p>", "timestamp": "16 January 2017"}
