{"name": "Steve Jones", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Warning- Beware of setting up direct debit with EnergyAustralia. <br> This company has been the hardest i have ever encountered to get services disconnected from. It has been over a month for me to receive a correct final bill for gas and electricity. They keep sending bills after the date of my cancellation and final reading, i have even received a bill starting after the date i moved out. Have made numerous phone calls to have these matters resolved and every time i get someone who is supposedly understanding however the same thing happens. Called again today to have these matters resolved so hopefully it will be sorted. A simple process that has been handled very poorly.</p>", "timestamp": "24 November 2016"}
