{"name": "Bellz Jay", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>worst service ever.<br> had us on the business rate for 12 months!! couldn't get anybody to change it from the first month we had it... now 12 months on they refuse to let us cancel the account while they try to work it out... except they wont work it out.<br> oh and lets not forget in june i was told we would get a full refund of all bills that had been paid... then apparently they have no notes on the account of that!! and now they tell us when we do cancel WE WILL OWE A CANCELLATI<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">ON FEE!!! <br> have been to the ombudsman with still no result.  and we cant open a new energy account for our new home because there is an ongoing dispute with these guys... but hang on... the person working on the dispute WENT ON ANNUAL LEAVE AND NOBODY ELSE CAN HANDLE THE MATTER!!! <br> we move out tomorrow. guess we'll be living in darkness until someone decides to give us the time of day. <br> never trust a multi million dollar vital company. they just dont care.</span></p>", "timestamp": "27 October 2016"}
