{"name": "Guy A Ogier", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Dear Energy Australia .... I have today received the 4th or 5th call about an overdue bill. I am called from the Philippines and despite me giving these people my new address to which I want the bill send several times, I am yet to receive the bill. Indeed, each new caller tells me he/she/it has no record of my new address. They have no correct email address and after three months, still; ... no bill. Seriously, your service, customer care and professionalism is a disgrace. The worst I have ever dealt with. Your reps are atrocious and your ability to meet my needs, adminstratively, non-existent. Disgrace!!!!!!!!!!!</p>", "timestamp": "10 October 2016"}
{"name": "Shani Duffin", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>What a joke! You guys turned our power off at midday today and with numerous phone calls you still can't give us a time when it will be turned on!!! All our food in the fridge and freezer is going to have to be put in the bin!! (I did the groceries yesterday!) We have no hot water to shower in the morning as we only have electricity where we live. This is ridiculous!! You guys stuffed up and we are the ones paying for it!! <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f8d/1/16/1f621.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\ude21</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f8d/1/16/1f621.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\ude21</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f8d/1/16/1f621.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\ude21</span></span></p>", "timestamp": "10 October 2016"}
