{"name": "Karli Anjoul", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/ohyehh?hc_ref=ARQmyvOHDC0VxiCOw0z26bbogez-EK05bxihOSvTUb_-9Lah5RuADBfSSK0G9Qv4SoY&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Last 16 months I have been extremely concerned with an ongoing issue due to confusion with estimated reads and a meter exchange which resulted in an extremely high bill . After many discussions with your solutions team and credit department with no resolution two days ago I was contacted by Anita in your resolution team.  My trust has been restored in your company. Anita followed through on her commitment to call me back with a resolution that was not only in the best interest of your company but also your customer. Thank you Anita for all your help. If only I had spoken to you 16 months ago. Thank you Energyaustralia it took a while but we got there in the end.</p>", "timestamp": "4 October 2016"}
