{"name": "Andrew Bazik", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>The incompetence of your company is outstanding. It has taken 3 months to get our gas swapped over and It has still not happened. I called up originally and set up the connection and after 2 weeks called back up and our details were not in the system. We then set it up again. After this, we were told we had to wait until the next meter reading, not a problem. That came and went, still not swapped over. We arranged for a special meter read, that went by and still we hadn't bee<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">n swapped over. I called up again and was told you do not do special meter reads, so we had to wait for the next standard meter read and guess what, shock horror, still not swapped over. Currently on phone to a member of your \"helpful\" staff who has stated that our currently Gas provider declined the swapover which was a lie, cause the next person I spoke to stated that our account was deleted and we have to set up again. after 30 minutes of tedious repetition the call dropped and we had to go through it again. Apparently we're now getting a special meter read and getting swapped over on October 4th (which is odd, cause EA previously stated that special meter reads for gas do not exist) although I will not hold my breath. At this point I don't know why we're bothering. Thanks for everything, keep up the good work. X x o <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"smile emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f4c/1/16/1f642.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"_7oe\">:)</span></span></span></p>", "timestamp": "28 September 2016"}
