{"name": "Ben Evans", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Interesting how my winter bill for just me this quarter is over $500. Especially considering I use one light and the TV at any given time and only use the heater when it's really cold. So sick and tired of paying over the top electricity bills. From my investigation it seems I pay the equivalent of a 4 person household even during 'non winter' periods. Unless I have 3 hobos living in my roof that I don't know about, then I'm being seriously overcharged. Definitely going to be shopping around. I just can't afford to be with Energy Australia anymore.</p>", "timestamp": "27 September 2016"}
{"name": "Morgana Creely", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Cratulations on the worst customer service ever to a new electrcity customer. I have already complained to several of your \"customer service\" reps with no avail, so don't tell me to call or use live chat. I've already wasted too much time getting the run around, conflicting information and multiple disconnected phone calls.</p>", "timestamp": "22 September 2016"}
{"name": "FeeFi Fiona", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Your customer service is not good...<br> Talked to young man today who couldn't have cared less ... then we got disconnected ....somehow ... did he bother to call back ?<br> Then spoke to another person ...asked about closing the account ... he didn't even ask why .... or anything ...<br> Having worked in CS .... I was always told to help the person on the phone ! They could not have cared at all ... <br> Looking for another company that isn't so expensive and better service ...</p>", "timestamp": "22 September 2016"}
