{"name": "Jessica Coulthard", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Trying to get our new gas meter installed has been an absolute farce, a comedy of errors, and a whole lot of passing the buck. I will be calling the ombudsman first thing Mondau for advice, after four booked in installations (two which apparently didn't exist in your system or were cancelled from your system, and two with rude and unhelpful contractors with very poor communication skills), I am left wondering how we are now going into our THIRD week without a gas meter and thus without hot water. Disgraceful, Energy Australia and APA.</p>", "timestamp": "9 September 2016"}
