{"name": "Justin Bryant-Smith", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>After following your IVR to speak to someone about payments the agent tells me I'm in the wrong area (so what's the point of the IVR???), transfers me to 'the right area' and then the call disconnects the second it goes through. Great way to waste my break!! Thanks Energy Australia! Considering how quick you are to send out bills &amp; reminder notices I would've thought you'd be more interested in speaking to people about payment than that...</p>", "timestamp": "8 September 2016"}
