{"name": "Bernard Gan", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Yesterday, Energy Australia instructed AUSGRID to knock on my parents' doors to inform them their account has been closed (Reasons still unknown, even though I always had direct debit for this account). Not long after, electricity was cut off immediately, leaving 2 old folks in sudden darkness, panicking and stressed for hours. </p>", "timestamp": "5 September 2016"}
