{"name": "Helen Moran", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>It would be really nice if you could give an ETA as to when the technician coming to read the meter is going to be at the property, even if it is a window of time.  I have called requesting a time to be told it isn't possible, surely the work can be planned to some sort of time frame.<br> Our meter is inaccessible due to it being at the back of the property and in the dog yard, so I fully understand why our bills are estimates and that we need to have the meter read once a year but as I have taken the day off work, it would be nice to be able to plan my day so I can make the most of it rather than sitting at home waiting for someone to arrive!  I am going to be mightily pissed if they turn up at 5pm!</p>", "timestamp": "11 August 2016"}
