{"name": "Andrew Sluggett", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/sluggett1?hc_ref=ARQeNQ-1Z5NDnmKxXkIx1KjvWQ8h-iwyK1tUOw36vsr78YN8CJ8S4PiG2sq1Ha3qT_w&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>3 times on the phone and every time i get transfered it hangs up. Gas bill sorted but trying to deal with the electricity bill and this happenes. Good work <span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f7d/1/16/1f44e.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\udc4e</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f7d/1/16/1f44e.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\udc4e</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f7d/1/16/1f44e.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\udc4e</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f7d/1/16/1f44e.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"_7oe\">\ud83d\udc4e</span></span></p>", "timestamp": "20 July 2016"}
{"name": "Ben Tobias", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/benscant?hc_ref=ARRAkCaSMAv37iuoWFXAQZ7ES5tKoqEFK7jp_juEbcLj4RnNrOFjI1glgF5xZvp_dDw&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Finally get my gas bill after a dispute lasting nearly a year and involving the ombudsman and the specified remedy has not been implemented.  When I call to query why, the \"systems are down\", with no ETA for a fix, and nothing can be done to sort it out until &lt;insert random inconvenient time here&gt;. The joke at my expense is wearing a bit thin now. Back to the ombudsman methinks, and a quick stop at some other retailers on the way to see if they can provide a better service... <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"unsure emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/ff2/1/16/1f615.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"_7oe\">:/</span></span></p>", "timestamp": "19 July 2016"}
{"name": "Ravi Tattitali", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/manish.das.77377?hc_ref=ARQp7h4BIx3RxpVeLH_kg4CyiSkYHPwRyOCNm1y58-eokONiyrBBuS3pWT1fC_I6SM4", "comment": "<p>Absolutely disgusting <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"/hashtag/energyaustralia?source=feed_text\" data-ft='{\"type\":104,\"tn\":\"*N\"}'><span class=\"_5afx\"><span aria-label=\"hashtag\" class=\"_58cl _5afz\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">energyaustralia</span></span></a>. You disconnected the power to our apartment without prior notice and despite having all our bills paid by direct debit. To top it all up we were talking to your customer service rep on the phone when they randomly disconnected the phone at 6.30pm to go home. Awesome customer service and complaint handling.  <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"/hashtag/forcedcandlelight?source=feed_text\" data-ft='{\"type\":104,\"tn\":\"*N\"}'><span class=\"_5afx\"><span aria-label=\"hashtag\" class=\"_58cl _5afz\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">forcedcandlelight</span></span></a>. Appalled by your shocking customer neglect !!! This is what my living room looks like ... we better get an explanation behind this !!!</p>", "timestamp": "14 July 2016"}
