{"name": "Amy Atama", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>I have had nothing but problems while with Energy Australia! Every bill is sent to the wrong address despite changing my address numerous times over the last 8 months.  Now issues with a payment due to a daily \"cut off\" time of when the payment was made. Customer service is appalling when trying to work out the issue.</p>", "timestamp": "26 June 2016"}
