{"name": "Guy Elsenburg", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/guy.elsenburg?hc_ref=ARRybnEnaPSPNipYjmMn5-qQgggYcFUgpq94yOBfRxpxthvXY7aX95p_xWhRh4wQReE&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>You are the worst company to go threw for gas and electricity you never get my mailing address right even though I call you constantly to get you to get it right and now you wait over a year to tell me I owe you money for a address I haven't been in for a long time ago you will be changing company and will tell everybody the troubles you have given me to deter them from going threw you</p>", "timestamp": "23 May 2016"}
