{"name": "Julie Favell", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/julie.favell.3?hc_ref=ARRxnkc5Jh_hzRJtH3cHTtDsSsFf09xQvjwN_IpHzV_LyPGBFWR80F6DpcWIG7lSgLE", "comment": "<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Australian-Energy-Storage-Conference-Exhibition-182565071916876/?ft%5Bqid%5D=6281308724415973347&amp;ft%5Bmf_story_key%5D=1214517779851023148&amp;ft%5Bego_id%5D=561380140702032&amp;ft%5Bei%5D=&amp;ft%5Bfbfeed_location%5D=1&amp;ft%5Binsertion_position%5D=1&amp;__md__=1\" data-ft='{\"tn\":\"-U\"}'>https://www.facebook.com/Australian-Energy-Storage-Confer\u2026/\u2026</a></p>", "timestamp": "5 May 2016"}
{"name": "Darren Fullerton", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/people/Darren-Fullerton/100010508168079?hc_ref=ARSC3PWbi6pwerG5fx8404NVRaak0Xi72Zp_IXhPA1EB9D7gpbtc-IDEzKcKwvHUOBA&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>\"Customers Beware\"<br> From our first experience with Energy Australia , we have had nothing but heart ache and sub standard service. <br> In 2012 Energy Australia approached my husband and I, to swap our energy suppliers to them. The customer service representative signed us up and said they would take care of the disconnection from our previous company which we thought was a huge stress off of us as we had just had our first child and were in the process of moving to a larger prope...</p>", "timestamp": "4 May 2016"}
{"name": "Gillian Prentice", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>So not impressed with Energy Australia. In about 2 months we have had 4 power outages, significant ones that have taken a fair amount of time to come back on.  I get that there was a storm last night but honestly every time it rains or there is a bit of wind we find ourselves saying \"Look out,  we will probably  lose power. \" 3 of those occasions were not due to wind or a storm and when calling the faults line,  no explanation was given.  We are living in the 21st century and we cannot even maintain consistent power usage to customers, what the heck is going on? We pay a lot of money for your service but it is not good enough.  We changed to you because your rates were cheaper. Think we know why the rates are cheaper.  Poor service.</p>", "timestamp": "30 April 2016"}
