{"name": "Wayne Li", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/people/Wayne-Li/100003916193407?hc_ref=ARTWQrfGfzp73efBO0ZRGPjdq9fKpoWA7I3DCpMGmF2E0VMVwfZR9PL5wY4Hckf4Enc&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Hi there. <br> I received my gas bill yesterday. According to the fantastic bill I've used 1218 cubic meters hot water in 66 days! That made me thought I owned a pool in my second floor APARTMENT! I mean seriously, there are only four people in my apartment and I can't figure out in which way could we use that much hot water. My former bills were just 30 cubic meters hot water per month. Could you kindly remind me how to fix this and get my correct bill? <br> Thank you.</p>", "timestamp": "21 April 2016"}
