{"name": "Cal Gillett", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/callum.gillett.1?hc_ref=ARTBijeh9DhJDL9QbxV2U9_3GG9pWD1BBJugsJCL0Oz66ho-6_QzOFyNqZ13OmZBKsI&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>How long is it going to take for power to be switched on? As it is 4 of my 7 fish tank air pumps are now destroyed because of water siphoning back into them from lack of power, are you going to pay for new ones? Also as they are tropical fish &amp; there is currently no heating for them if they happen to die from cold water are you going to pay for them too? Are you also going to replace the food in my fridge/freezer that is spoilt?</p>", "timestamp": "18 April 2016"}
