{"name": "Cameron McGregor", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/cameron.mcgregor.7?hc_ref=ARRN0e0P6QrkFB5YhEVUlRkcx2pXvyAScY4Xg-7l8MGsQQzpkmRaK0FPmToly_0yOHo&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Organized for gas to be connected last Monday 11/4/16. Told it would be connected by Thursday 14/4/16 at the latest. Still no gas!!!!!!! No hot water and can't cook!!! I'm extremely annoyed as I have two young children!!!!<br> Called several times regarding the matter but told the job has not been entered in the system to be done!!!!</p>", "timestamp": "17 April 2016"}
