{"name": "Nancy Uz", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>So sick of having to call up EVERY billing cycle and sort out this companies faults. I don't have time to sit on the phone and tell people how to do their job. The last bill that I was overcharged for had to be explained to 3 different people before someone worked it out. Then i was finally given the option of having the money refunded into my credit card, or credited into my next bill. I chose the refund option as I knew how unreliable this company was. However this never ha<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">ppened and i was unable to follow up as i had recently given birth to my second child. I would have assumed this would then at least be credited in my next bill WHICH NEVER HAPPENED!! I have also been incorrectly charged AGAIN for this cycle and still owed this money. I am sick to death of having to call this incompetent company after every bill i recieve because the discounts aren't applied correctly. I will be searching for a new provider, this is ridiculous!!!</span></p>", "timestamp": "13 April 2016"}
{"name": "Deborah Hughes", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/deborah.hughes.9081?hc_ref=ARTHeG8CHH__K-t1h4Q1R0qe6SepIzMk0ZkgVPdXIxDdq6mH2nqFGnrqDEL_LJhaSoc&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>It's a sad state of affairs when you have 10% charge left on your iPhone, you fed your puppy (because she comes first) by your iPhone light - the best Energy Australia can do is yes we know and it will be a few more hours <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"/hashtag/firstworldproblems?source=feed_text\" data-ft='{\"type\":104,\"tn\":\"*N\"}'><span class=\"_5afx\"><span aria-label=\"hashtag\" class=\"_58cl _5afz\">#</span><span class=\"_58cm\">firstworldproblems</span></span></a> until you kinda sorta regain power</p>", "timestamp": "13 April 2016"}
