{"name": "Kylie Watt", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Oh my god how difficult is it for bills to be emailed??? Since I switched not one had been received but you have no issues sending those late payment letters! I am so angry about this, and also that I can't speak to anyone at 6.30pm WHEN I GET HOME. I can't recall if I am on a contract, but if I'm not, I'll be taking my business elsewhere.</p>", "timestamp": "11 April 2016"}
{"name": "Gina Bullians", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/gina.bullians?hc_ref=ARQr2ppvhRwkcv1O1DtEvN1-17eTRyLYdQcwVXpvtpqmsXAkm6EjMXP9-0l_4acDm5k&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Have had the worst experience with Energy Australia, and will be changing providers.  The fact that you can never get in touch with anyone that can help and I am sick to death of overseas call centres, with no customer skills, no empathy and no ability to sort out issues.  All I want to do is speak to someone in Australia.  Thanks anyway EA, will look for another provide, who is hopefully easier to deal with <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"unsure emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" height=\"16\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/ff2/1/16/1f615.png\" width=\"16\" alt=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"_7oe\">:/</span></span></p>", "timestamp": "10 April 2016"}
{"name": "Jodie Williams", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/jodie.williams.5688?hc_ref=ARTfve5D3AN8IiZNzQHV0DSxGRf0rYAT88KiRH4rXntPmHLydCEVBvR-pocbso2O03g&fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Energy Australia!! To say I'm frustrated and over it is an understatement!! I had an account with you then I moved. Advised you of this. You did a final reading and then after numerous phone calls to ask where my final bill was I got it about 4 months later. Moving on from this I asked for an extension to pay which was granted and a letter to state this sent out. While this extension was in place I received numerous calls from you demanding payment. Also text messages. When I<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"> called back they would say, oh sorry about that don't know why it's happening I see you have an extension. GUESS WHAT??? More calls and texts demanding payment. I then paid the bill when it was due and got another 2 phone calls. And today I get my mail and receive a letter from recoveries Corp demanding payment as you have escalated the matter to them!!! What a joke! The bill is paid and this is still going on!! What is going on there? It's a bloody Joke. Get your act together. I'm sure it's not just me. Talk about ridiculous.</span></p>", "timestamp": "7 April 2016"}
