{"name": "Janine Bergin", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Wow whatever you do, DO NOT ever use Energy Australia. Booked to have both my gas and electricity connected today for my new home. Every day this week I have had to spend over an hour on the phone to their call centre as they cancelled my gas connection (without advising me!). So after being reassured each day that everything is sorted out and ready, they now tell me that one of their departments forgot to submit the paperwork and I'll have to wait until next Wednesday for installation!!!! Still on the phone trying to sort it out. What a bunch of morons.....the worst customer service I have EVER experienced</p>", "timestamp": "21 January 2016"}
{"name": "Christie McFadden", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>Energy Australia I am extremely disappointed in how you have treated my step son who has requested a new connection with you in Corio 3214. He moved in last Friday (7 Full days ago) and whilst you did connect his power on Friday he is still waiting on a gas connection. 7 days of living in a new house with 3 kids (8,6 and 3) and not a drop of hot water to either bath them or wash dishes/ clothes. We spoke to you yesterday on his behalf with him there and you assured us that it<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"> was the distributors issue and that everything had been sorted and 100% he would have his gas connected today. Imagine our surprise when we finish work and find out yet again you have let him down and he is still without gas to run his hot water service. This is simply not good enough, especially with 3 young kids. Apparently the issue lies with the service being blocked, assumedly because the previous customer didn't pay their bills, how this is now his issue makes no sense at all. You are required to establish a connection to an existing property within one business day of being given notice (prior to 3pm the day before) he signed up for a connection with you on Monday the 11th of January, please explain to me why this has not occurred and why you gave us a guarantee yesterday that it would be done today and it hasn't been. Very disappointed.</span></p>", "timestamp": "21 January 2016"}
