{"name": "Ross Ensbey", "link": "https://www.facebook.com/EnergyAustralia/?fref=nf", "comment": "<p>I have called up FIVE times to transfer the gas hot water from a previous tenant into my name and you have CATEGORICALLY FAILED to successfully do this. Instead, despite me wasting HOURS and HOURS or my time calling you and you promising every time to get it right, you KEEP sending the bill to the old tenant who doesn't even live in Australia anymore! What sort of ridiculous company are you when I call up and let you know there is no possible way to get money from an old tena<span class=\"text_exposed_hide\">...</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">nt with no forwarding address and that I WANT TO GIVE YOU MY MONEY INSTEAD AND PAY MY BILLS and you cannot get this right?! FIVE TIMES!!!!! This is unbelievably bad. This is like me walking up to someone and BEGGING them to take my money and the person failing to be competent enough to even take it! Are you SERIOUS?! IF I GET ANOTHER BILL IN THE PREVIOUS TENANTS NAME OR ANOTHER THREAT TO CUT OFF MY HOT WATER I WILL LOSE MY MIND! This, plus last time I dealt with Energy Australia for a bill dispute on electricity it took you OVER TWELVE MONTHS to resolve!! How the hell are you in business?!</span></p>", "timestamp": "18 January 2016"}
